Property Brothers at Home - Season 3, Episode 5 (Drew's Honeymoon House)




Great Outdoors

Drew and his fiancee Linda race to renovate their vintage Los Angeles home on a tight 12-week deadline ahead of a pre-wedding party. The inside transformation is complete and now Jonathan and Drew are ready to tackle the outdoor spaces. They restore the house's front according to strict historical guidelines, turn the backyard into a poolside oasis and create a breathtaking third-floor deck. Finally, Drew and Linda's family and friends arrive for an epic party celebrating their upcoming wedding.




Original Air Date: 20-Dec-2017
